  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE THE BOARD OF SUPERVISORS OF PERRY COUNTY, MISSISSIPPI, TO ASSESS A CERTAIN FEE FOR ANY CIVIL CASE FILED AND ANY MISDEMEANOR CONVICTION AND/OR ADJUDICATION OBTAINED IN THE JUSTICE COURT OF THE COUNTY TO FUND THE REPAIRS, RECONSTRUCTION, OPERATION, FURNISHING, TECHNOLOGY AND MAINTENANCE OF THE PERRY COUNTY JUSTICE COURT BUILDING; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
